{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事米蘭稱他將支持降息半個百分點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會理事斯蒂芬·米蘭表示，他將支持本月降息半個百分點，並重申貿易緊張局勢給經濟帶來不確定性，增加了經濟成長的下行風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">米蘭周四在接受福克斯商業頻道採訪時稱，「如果貨幣政策保持當前的緊縮程度，而經濟遭遇此類衝擊，那麼衝擊的負面後果將顯著加劇。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充稱，在10月28-29日會議上將支持降息半個百分點，儘管委員會可能如9月般僅降息0.25個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為今年可能實施三次25個基點的降息，」他說道。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a637698d-e7e5-33f8-8620-24ded5a1cd7d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：聯儲會理事米蘭：貿易不確定性令降息更顯迫切</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾暗示，鑒於招聘放緩可能推高失業率，央行本月有望實施25個基點降息。但部分決策者仍強調需保持審慎，因通膨率仍然高於2%的目標水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Miran Says He Would Favor Half-Point Interest Rate Cut</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E7%B1%B3%E8%98%AD%E7%A8%B1%E4%BB%96%E5%B0%87%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%80%8B%E7%99%BE%E5%88%86%E9%BB%9E-121718671.html",
