        {
            "title": "貿易戰火升高下 亞洲大型經濟體外匯官員以攻代守",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MK9hReO9qrLSZ.bSA8ZSNQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/80e3f4596b0c100cc6160eda2f39c9bd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著貿易戰愈演愈烈，亞洲大型經濟體的政策制定者本周紛紛出手強力捍衛本國貨幣；策略師表示，他們的任務才剛剛開始。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國、印度、日本和韓國的官員已透過口頭和行動支持本國貨幣——市場參與者表示，隨著美國的貿易戰有可能重創經濟成長，這些國家是在先發制人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一位知情人士表示，印度央行在境內和境外市場拋售美元，以反制對盧比的投機性攻擊。中國周四將人民幣兌美元中間價調升至一年來最強水平；韓國則口頭干預，表示正在關注韓元匯率的單邊波動。日本當局強調，匯率維持穩定走勢很重要。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f56db2d4-978a-361a-bc1f-48ff56fb4868-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">富國銀行駐紐約策略師Brendan McKenna表示，中美緊張局勢的最新升級正在影響印度盧比、韓元和人民幣的市場情緒，沒有一家央行願意承擔資本外流或輸入型通膨的風險。McKenna表示，可能會看到中國人民銀行和印度央行採取最強硬的防禦措施，韓國央行料也將積極應對。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9lFsk7vlEXe_3FC.4mOqAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b589159ada7a6385aeac767e537aff80\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Currency Officials Go on Offensive as Trade Angst in Asia Mounts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%87%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8B-%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%AB%94%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BB%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%88-065450253.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-16 15:25:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新加坡主權財富基金GIC在美國起訴蔚來 提出虛增收入指控",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 新加坡主權財富基金在美國一家法院起訴蔚來，指控這家中國電動汽車製造商及其高管虛增收入、違反證券法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">訴訟於8月在紐約南區法院提起，蔚來及其執行長李斌、前財務長奉瑋被列為被告。蔚來股價周四在香港和新加坡市場均一度下跌逾13%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府投資公司(GIC)指控這些被告就蔚來與其關聯公司蔚能的關係作出了「重大虛假和/或誤導性陳述」，並且未能披露有關其業務和財務的關鍵事實。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據訴狀，這些不實陳述讓蔚來汽車證券價值被誇大，導致GIC遭受「重大損失」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-545abc10-2e47-3ff7-8de7-87b8fe692a69-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蔚來採取的是電池租用服務(BaaS)模式，即購車者無需直接購買電池，而是支付一定費用，即可使用蔚來的換電網絡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">GIC起訴稱，蔚能的財務記錄顯示，該公司預先從蔚來購買了電池，讓蔚來得以立即記錄這些銷售的全額收入，而終端用戶卻尚未付費。訴狀稱，此類收入應該逐步確認，而不是一次性確認。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蔚來汽車尚未回應置評請求。GIC拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題GIC Sues China EV Maker Nio in US, Alleging Inflated Revenue (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 David Ramli、Felix Tam.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91gic%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E8%94%9A%E4%BE%86-%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%99%9B%E5%A2%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7-060053322.html",
